address: Khu II, ƒê. 3 Th√°ng 2, Xu√¢n Kh√°nh, Ninh Ki·ªÅu, C·∫ßn Th∆°
comment: Can Tho University - where you will find everything, from stressful classes to equally interesting and relaxing "off" sessions. The special thing is, if you walk through the campus, you will understand what "studying hard" means when you have to try not to get lost in the vast campus like a maze. But don't worry, just walk around and you'll meet new friends - because this place is famous for its friendly spirit of exchange.  The lecturers here are quite enthusiastic, sometimes so "hot" that you have to applaud their "super" communication ability, but if you happen to be late, don't forget to prepare yourself mentally, because their "enthusiasm" sometimes even surpasses the limits of the subject! And in terms of facilities, the school may not be too luxurious, but you will always find a cozy study corner, or at least a seat enough to "rest" while studying.  Can Tho University is a place where you can both "bury your head" in books and enjoy moments of Western-style relaxation.

address: Khu II, ƒê. 3 Th√°ng 2, Xu√¢n Kh√°nh, Ninh Ki·ªÅu, C·∫ßn Th∆°
comment: Really impressed with the school's large campus and dynamic academic environment. The school is not only famous for its educational quality but is also an ideal tourist destination with unique architectural works and lush green gardens. Can Tho University is not only a leading training place in the South but also a cultural symbol, a place that preserves traditional values combined with the spirit of innovation and creativity. A memorable destination for anyone looking to explore culture and education.

comment: Can Tho University can be considered the school with the longest history in the Mekong Delta. The school is considered an educational training center in the West. Teachers here are Professors, Associate Professors, Doctors, and Masters with very high expertise and extensive experience. Many successful students in life are trained from this school.  Head of CTU has a very large area. Including the largest area 2 at 3/2 Can Tho street. Area 1 is located on Ly Tu Trong street, area 3 in Hoa An and a new area in Mang Den.  The school offers multi-disciplinary training but the strongest is Agriculture and Fisheries with huge investment. This can be a great choice for young people studying in Can Tho and having high expertise in the future.
